::Shadow Wing::

She calmed down after a bit.  She would have to learn to control her 
emotions.  But for now, she had gotten it out of her system.  She 
decided to talk to Lunarpine and see what he was thinking.  After 
all, she thought, he must have heard me pounding on the walls.

She unlocked her room door and opened it.  She walked down the hall 
towards the engine room to find Lunarpine.
